    "violates the Illegal Activities scenario (IA), and should not elicit a meaningful \"answer\".",
    "For simplicity, we refer to these contexts as \"scenarios\", the inquiries made to ChatGPT as \"questions\", and the responses generated by ChatGPT as \"answers\" throughout this paper.",
    "Motivating ExampleIn Figure 1, we present a motivating example to demonstrate the restrictions imposed on ChatGPT by OpenAI, and how a jailbreak prompt can bypass these restrictions to obtain desired results from the model.",
    "Figure 1 illustrates the conversations between the user and ChatGPT before and after jailbreak.In the normal mode without jailbreak, the user asks ChatGPT a question about creating and distributing malware for financial gain.",
    "However, this question, which pertains to Illegal Activities (IA), violates OpenAI's policy [4]."
